# Tools

- Reddit JSON uses disk cache under `~/.avcm-cache/reddit/` with backoff on HTTP errors.
- Memory tools must align metadata keys with `memory/schema.py`.
- **Instagram / Apify**: before changing `instagram_apify_tool.py`, use **`user-apify` MCP** (`search-actors`, `fetch-actor-details`) so `run_input` matches the actor schema. Reddit/Serper tools never require Apify.
